#      Internal UTF-8 encoding helpers used by node:buffer shim.
#
#   3. Source transform hook for TypeScript support
#      std._setSourceTransform(fn) — JS API for registering transforms
#      js_std_apply_source_transform() — C API for applying the hook
#      js_std_set_source_transform_fn() — C API for setting the hook
#      Used by bootstrap.js (runtime) and qnc.c (compile time).
#
#   4. Sandbox integration hooks (when USE_SANDBOX is defined)
#      - js_std_get_port_list() accessor for worker message ports
#      - js_sandbox_init() and js_sandbox_add_export() hooks
#
